OL,5, The boss of Centrica, the energy giant 
OL,6, which owns British Gas, has seen his   
OL,7, pay package rise by almost #4m.        
OL,9,FChris O'Shea's remuneration was #8.2m  
OL,10,Fin 2023, up from #4.5m in 2022,        
OL,11,Faccording to the firm's annual report. 
OL,13,FThe package consists of a salary of    
OL,14,F#810,000, a #1.4m annual bonus and     
OL,15,F#5.9m in long-term bonus, pension and  
OL,16,Fbenefits.                              
OL,18,FIn January, Mr O'Shea told the BBC his 
OL,19,Fpay was "impossible to justify".       
